long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Gitsight derives insights from open source repositories and their contributors.
With our extension, you will have at your fingertips a reliable understanding of a developer's OSS contributions while browsing github profiles or reading emails from a candidate developer.
Quickly assess profiles without leaving your email, easily share the information with your colleagues, and build rapport with developers thanks to Gitsight insights.
Gitsight is the perfect companion to the technical recruiter that wants to move fast and gather useful and reliable information to have complete candidate profiles.
